body:
@zou3519 I'm using Wide ResNet 50-2. 
But I reproduced same behavior for simple ResNet-50 from torchvision with same code as I wrote above with results: 13.89 msec for Python and 33 msec for C++.

My Wide ResNet 50-2 was converted from old torch. Code of this model is in file wideresnet.py in
[pytorch-issue.zip](https://github.com/pytorch/pytorch/files/2588737/pytorch-issue.zip). Also there is a file of my model in mymodel.py which based on wideresnet.py.

Model was converted to torchscript by the code in the first snippet in the issue body.
